<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212403>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Siconema ovicallosum sp. n. A – G, female; H – K, male. A: entire worm; B: pharynx region; C: posterior region; D: vulval region; E: eggs; F: tail tip; G: hooks; H: entire worm; I: pharynx region; J: cloaca; K: caudal organ. All in lateral position. Scale bars in µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212403/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212404>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Siconema ovicallosum sp. n. SEM images. Female. A, B: head hooks, latero-dorsal view; C: caudal organ, ventral view; D: amphid, lateral view. Scale bars in µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212404/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

